###1、 flutter: command not found
export PATH="/Users/chenjc/flutter/bin":$PATH
2、flutter pub get 时卡住：Running "flutter pub get" in xxx...
进入项目目录，输入以下内容：
export PUB_HOSTED_URL=https://pub.flutter-io.cn
 export FLUTTER_STORAGE_BASE_URL=https://storage.flutter-io.cn
 
 中国镜像：https://flutter.cn/community/china

